            <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
              The NavHeader component can be easily customized by editing:
            </p>
            <code class="block bg-neutral-900 text-green-400 p-4 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm">
              /src/components/ui/nav-header.tsx
            </code>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-8 shadow-lg border border-neutral-200">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-neutral-900">Scroll Test</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-700">
              Scroll down to see how the navigation stays fixed at the top of the viewport.
            </p>
          </div>

